	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />In the end all graphics were reduced to 4bpp (16 color) SNES tiles. The technology is in the process of taking those 3D renders and getting them down to usable standard SNES graphics.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


