	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />"ACM" was just a marketing term (like Blast Processing) used to hype the game's extensive use of pre-rendered 3D graphics, something which was relatively new to console games. None of the three DKC games used any special mapper hardware or anything.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


